metadata.description:
behold and brace yourself, welcome to the magnifent gorga island, land of the supranatural being that live in pure joy and full of strong connection with each others family member

Indonesia has more than 360 ethnic groups and actually thats my main goal, to explore all of it and execute it on my artwork, so all of the world could enjoy the beauty but with psychedelic art style composition
